  <summary date="2020-08-20T19:57:02Z" status="Introduced in House">Help End Abusive Living Situations Act or the HEALS Act

This bill requires the Department of Housing and Urban Development to consider the needs of survivors of domestic violence, dating violence, sexual assault, and stalking when awarding grants under the Continuum of Care Program, which provides funding for nonprofit providers and state and local governments&#160;to quickly rehouse homeless individuals&#160;and families.</summary>
